{"tid":567281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【$4萬變$156萬】台高中生投資比特幣狂賺 夠交4年大學學費","createTime":"2018-02-20T17:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T01:32:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"203ba22b986755d01fb180b88b068ff3857dc6d7","tid":567281,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T17:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180221/large/1519142565_6aa1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180221%2Flarge%2F1519142565_6aa1.jpg&h=1c0cdc7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正所謂有危就有機，虛擬貨幣比特幣（bitcoin）近年幣值大起大落，一名在台灣高中生就靠着投資比特幣，賺取4年美國大學學費。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約郵報》報道，22歲紐約大學學生陳柯尼（Konig Chen，音譯），日前公開他投資比特幣獲利的經驗。報道稱，在巴西成長、台灣讀高中的陳柯尼，去年2月始投資比特幣，他先投資5,000美元（39,118港元），接着比特幣幣值一路狂飆，直至去年底，陳柯尼手上的比特幣已經價值20萬美元（156.4萬港元）。這筆錢足夠讓陳柯尼負擔4年紐約大學學費。<br />\n<br />\n陳柯尼將投資成功歸功於同學研究出的演算法，據說共有15人在該名學生的操盤下大賺一筆。比特幣市值最近雖然一路下跌，但攻讀酒店管理的陳柯尼仍看好虛擬貨幣的未來：「賺過這麼多錢之後，我已經不想當酒店經理人了。我的計畫是繼續賺錢，然後買下一間渡假村。」不過，買賣這類虛擬貨幣，風險極高，投資者還是要量力而為。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約郵報》/ 台灣《蘋果日報》"},{"pid":"dc1df5c86cadf8f23beb0de3e11d327d46b78176","tid":567281,"uid":169220,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T17:18:15.000Z","msg":"炒賣投機當投資都好拎黎曬名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dee8fc43783416734f7d9d45cadbc9e440887fc7","tid":567281,"uid":88029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T17:22:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64c90fb39e3dbdd734a2076217811b49ca6e0782","tid":567281,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T19:12:19.000Z","msg":"係咪媒來<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2548e47c4bd916bff37fe2a402435da7a83d32a1","tid":567281,"uid":61271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T19:36:26.000Z","msg":"勿眼紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2535a2bb1c86feca17a72481efe7b6cd6bb707cb","tid":567281,"uid":29514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T23:58:39.000Z","msg":"普通高中生邊到黎4皮野少bitcoin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bccc3042de0a5f3898a5b1a597bffe41b18ab81f","tid":567281,"uid":153592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T00:16:22.000Z","msg":"因為 啊！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02bbbf241c285fe0e95f3b0832f0e71913238e7","tid":567281,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T01:32:52.000Z","msg":"家底應該有米 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}